body:
Fractal Industry (or Fracdustry) is a newly-made technology mod in Forge 1.17.1.

❗[Geckolib](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/geckolib) is required!

In the early stage of development, many features are not implemented and we don't ensure its stability :(

(So BACKUP your world before applying the mod! BACK-IT-UP!).



Below are some features we have planned:

Implemented✔:

Ore Generation(Bauxite, cassiterite, ilmenite, spodumene ores together with their deepslate variants);

Power Generator(Thermal Generator and Microwave Generator);

Machines(Ore Processor);

Ingots and respective armors&tools.

Energy Cable;

Work In Progress🔧:


More complex&immersive crafting recipes;

Electrical Furnace and other functional machines;

Future Plan📚:


Various tools and armors;
Anything reasonable to implement...



Attention❗:

The mod introduced simple PBR textures, open your shader for a better visual experience :D (We highly recommend [Continuum](https://continuum.graphics/)!)

JEI is highly recommended to be installed to check the recipes.

The mod is UNSTABLE, but you can always get the latest build on [Github Actions](https://github.com/welancraft/fracdustry/actions)!

We of the Team Fractal are new to Minecraft modding, so it's welcome to visit our repository and leave your valuable opinion(Show us some mercy when you criticize~)

You definitely CAN add the mod to your modpack, but it's better to do it when the mod is stabilized and officially released. We will be glad if the names of the author/team are noted in your modpack's info!
